# ⭐ SAHAN DATA

**SAHAN DATA** is a web platform where users can purchase data packages and call minutes, earn rewards through referrals and promo codes, and compete in weekly, monthly, and annual leaderboards. The system is built with a **Supabase backend** (PostgreSQL) and a **static frontend** (HTML/CSS/JS) deployed on GitHub Pages.

