## 🚀 Features

- User registration & login via **email/password** or **promo code** (acts as username)
- Purchase data packages using a **5-step wizard** (provider → service → plan → payment method → sender/receiver + promo code)
- **USSD auto-dial** after successful order
- **Referral system** – each user gets a unique 6‑character referral code and a shareable link
- **Promo code system** – sequential numeric code (1,2,3,…) used during checkout to track promotions
- **Leaderboards** – top referrers (weekly), top sellers & top promoted (monthly), top districts/groups/schools
- **Reward distribution** – bonus points, free packages, and certificates awarded automatically via RPC functions
- **Admin panel** – manage orders and products (admin only)
- **Real‑time order feed** on the homepage
- **Mobile‑responsive** glassmorphism design

