## 🗄 Backend Schema

### 1. `customers` – user profiles

| Column               | Type        | Constraints                                 |
|----------------------|-------------|---------------------------------------------|
| `id`                 | UUID        | PRIMARY KEY                                 |
| `uid`                | UUID        | NOT NULL, UNIQUE, REFERENCES `auth.users`   |
| `full_name`          | TEXT        | NOT NULL                                    |
| `phone_number`       | TEXT        | NOT NULL, UNIQUE, CHECK (Somali format)     |
| `email`              | TEXT        | UNIQUE                                      |
| `district`           | TEXT        | NOT NULL                                    |
| `group_code`         | CHAR(1)     | NOT NULL, CHECK (A–Y)                       |
| `school`             | TEXT        | NOT NULL                                    |
| `referral_code`      | CHAR(6)     | NOT NULL, UNIQUE                            |
| `promo_code`         | TEXT        | NOT NULL, UNIQUE (sequential 1,2,3,…)       |
| `referred_by`        | UUID        | NULL, REFERENCES `customers(id)`            |
| `status`             | TEXT        | DEFAULT 'active'                            |
| `total_referrals`    | INT         | DEFAULT 0                                   |
| `bonus_points`       | INT         | DEFAULT 0                                   |
| `free_package_claimed`| DATE       | NULL                                        |
| `created_at`         | TIMESTAMPTZ | DEFAULT now()                               |

### 2. `products` – available data packages

| Column         | Type          | Constraints            |
|----------------|---------------|------------------------|
| `id`           | SERIAL        | PRIMARY KEY            |
| `name`         | VARCHAR(100)  | NOT NULL               |
| `provider`     | VARCHAR(50)   | NOT NULL               |
| `price`        | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL, CHECK (>0)   |
| `amount_cents` | INT           | NOT NULL, CHECK (>0)   |
| `image_url`    | TEXT          | NULL                   |

### 3. `orders` – purchase records

| Column           | Type         | Constraints                                  |
|------------------|--------------|----------------------------------------------|
| `id`             | UUID         | PRIMARY KEY                                  |
| `order_number`   | VARCHAR(20)  | NOT NULL, UNIQUE                             |
| `customer_id`    | UUID         | NULL, REFERENCES `customers(id)`             |
| `customer_phone` | VARCHAR(20)  | NOT NULL, CHECK (Somali format)              |
| `product_id`     | INT          | NOT NULL, REFERENCES `products(id)`          |
| `amount`         | DECIMAL(10,2)| NOT NULL                                     |
| `promo_code`     | TEXT         | NULL, REFERENCES `customers(promo_code)`     |
| `status`         | VARCHAR(20)  | DEFAULT 'completed'                          |
| `created_at`     | TIMESTAMPTZ  | DEFAULT now()                                |
| `receiver_phone` | VARCHAR(20)  | NULL (for gift orders)                       |

### 4. `transactions` – reward/commission tracking

| Column        | Type         | Constraints                                                      |
|---------------|--------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
| `id`          | UUID         | PRIMARY KEY                                                      |
| `customer_id` | UUID         | NOT NULL, REFERENCES `customers(id)`                             |
| `type`        | VARCHAR(20)  | NOT NULL, CHECK (`buyer`,`district`,`group`,`school`,`referral`,`promo`) |
| `order_id`    | UUID         | NOT NULL, REFERENCES `orders(id)`                                |
| `created_at`  | TIMESTAMPTZ  | DEFAULT now()                                                    |

### 5. `rewards` – competition winners

| Column             | Type         | Constraints                                  |
|--------------------|--------------|----------------------------------------------|
| `id`               | UUID         | PRIMARY KEY                                  |
| `competition_type` | TEXT         | NOT NULL                                     |
| `period_year`      | INT          | NOT NULL                                     |
| `period_month`     | INT          | NULL                                         |
| `period_week`      | INT          | NULL                                         |
| `winner_id`        | UUID         | NULL, REFERENCES `customers(id)`             |
| `winner_name`      | TEXT         | NULL                                         |
| `winner_value`     | TEXT         | NULL                                         |
| `total_count`      | BIGINT       | NOT NULL                                     |
| `awarded_at`       | TIMESTAMPTZ  | DEFAULT now()                                |

### Triggers

- **`trigger_update_total_referrals`** – After a new user inserts with a `referred_by` value, automatically increments the referrer’s `total_referrals`.

