## 📞 RPC Functions (Stored Procedures)

All RPC functions are created with `SECURITY DEFINER` to bypass RLS where needed.

### Core Functions

| #   | Function Name                       | Purpose                                                           |
|-----|-------------------------------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|
| 1   | `register_customer`                 | Registers a new user, auto‑generates `promo_code` (sequence), `referral_code` (random 6), `group_code` (A–Y cycle). |
| 2   | `create_order`                      | Creates an order, records transaction, prevents self‑promo code usage, returns USSD code. |

### Leaderboard Functions (Top 5 or Top 3)

| #   | Function Name                       | Returns                                                          |
|-----|-------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
| 3   | `get_weekly_top_referrers`          | Top 3 referrers of the current week (weekly competition).        |
| 4   | `get_monthly_top_promoted`          | Top 5 users whose promo code was used most in a given month.     |
| 5   | `get_monthly_top_seller`            | Top 5 users with most orders in a given month.                   |
| 6   | `get_top_sellers`                   | Top 5 sellers of all time.                                       |
| 7   | `get_top_promoted`                  | Top 5 promo codes of all time.                                   |
| 8   | `get_top_districts`                 | Top 5 districts by number of orders.                             |
| 9   | `get_top_groups`                    | Top 5 groups (`group_code`) by orders.                           |
| 10  | `get_top_schools`                   | Top 5 schools by orders.                                         |

### Statistics Functions

| #   | Function Name                       | Returns                                                          |
|-----|-------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
| 11  | `get_total_users`                   | Total number of customers.                                       |
| 12  | `get_total_orders`                  | Total number of orders.                                          |
| 13  | `get_total_transactions`            | Total number of transactions.                                    |
| 14  | `get_total_referrals_sum`           | Sum of all `total_referrals`.                                    |
| 15  | `get_total_districts`               | Number of distinct districts.                                    |
| 16  | `get_total_groups`                  | Number of distinct group codes.                                  |
| 17  | `get_total_schools`                 | Number of distinct schools.                                      |

### Award Functions (Reward Distribution)

| #   | Function Name                       | Reward                                                           |
|-----|-------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------|
| 18  | `award_weekly_top_referrer`         | +100 points + free package + certificate to weekly top referrer. |
| 19  | `award_monthly_promoted`            | +100 points + free package + certificate to monthly top promoted.|
| 20  | `award_monthly_top_seller`          | +100 points to monthly top seller.                               |
| 21  | `award_annual_top_district`         | Trophy to district with most orders in the year.                 |
| 22  | `award_annual_top_group`            | Trophy to group with most orders in the year.                    |
| 23  | `award_annual_top_school`           | Trophy to school with most orders in the year.                   |

