## 🏆 Reward System

| Competition       | Frequency | Winners | Prize                                                                 |
|-------------------|-----------|---------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Most referrals    | Weekly    | 1st     | 100 bonus points + free package + certificate                         |
| Most promoted (promo code usage) | Monthly | 1st | 100 bonus points + free package + certificate                         |
| Most seller (orders) | Monthly | 1st | 100 bonus points                                                      |
| Top district      | Annually  | 1       | Trophy                                                                |
| Top group         | Annually  | 1       | Trophy                                                                |
| Top school        | Annually  | 1       | Trophy                                                                |

Winners are stored in the `rewards` table via the respective `award_...` RPC functions.

