## 🚢 Deployment

The project is deployed on **GitHub Pages**:

- **Live URL**: [https://sahandata.github.io/Sahan/](https://sahandata.github.io/Sahan/)
- **Repository**: [https://github.com/sahandata/Sahan](https://github.com/sahandata/Sahan)

To deploy your own instance:

1. Clone the repository.
2. Update `SUPABASE_URL` and `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` in all HTML files (search for `YOUR_PROJECT` placeholders).
3. Run the provided SQL scripts (schema, RPC functions, triggers) in your Supabase SQL Editor.
4. Push to a GitHub repository and enable GitHub Pages in the repository settings (branch `main`, root folder).

